@data.characters.f3_mother.name: Come on, @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name, it's time to get ready for bed.

@data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name: But I still have so much homework to do!

@data.characters.f3_mother.name: Hm, this is the third night in a row that you haven’t gone to bed on time because of homework.

@data.characters.f3_mother.name: "How can we make sure you get all your work done and still get to bed on time?”

@data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name: “Maybe I can start earlier?”

 @data.characters.f3_mother.name: “Shall we make a rule that you start your homework half an hour after you get home from school? That way, you can finish it and have some time to relax before bed, too! I am happy to help you a little bit.”

 @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name: “Okay, @data.characters.f3_mother.name.”

*The next day.*

 @data.characters.f3_mother.name: “@data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name, have you started your homework yet?”

 @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name: “I'll start now, @data.characters.f3_mother.name! Can I talk to you about this question?”

 @data.characters.f3_mother.name: “Of course, my dear.”

*Later that same day.*

 @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name: “Look, @data.characters.f3_mother.name, I'm ready for bed so early tonight!”

 @data.characters.f3_mother.name: “Well done, @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name. Thank you for working with me to find a solution that works. Now you can be well-rested for tomorrow!”
